- Yong-san!

949
01:02:02,316 --> 01:02:03,776
Saya ada di sini!

950
01:02:09,198 --> 01:02:11,534
- Di mana?
- Saya tak boleh buka mata!

951
01:02:12,702 --> 01:02:15,705
