973
01:03:36,369 --> 01:03:38,829
- Saya boleh buka mata?
- Ya. Macam mana?

974
01:03:39,789 --> 01:03:40,706
Awak boleh melihat?

975
01:03:42,166 --> 01:03:43,376
Ya!

976
01:03:43,876 --> 01:03:45,461
Doktor, saya dah nampak!

977
01:03:48,255 --> 01:03:50,633
- Hei!
- Hei!

978
01:03:52,927 --> 01:03:56,347
